Description:
    Amahi plugin generator

    Creates a new plugin and its views. Pass the plugin name as the first argument.

Example:
    `rails generate plugin Thing`
    
    or multiple words joined with underscore 
    `rails generate plugin any_thing`
    
    or CamelCased phrases 
    `rails generate plugin AnyThing`
  
     This will create a basic Amahi platform plugin with URL like /tab/things.

        Controller: plugins/things/app/controllers/things_controller.rb
        Route:      plugins/things/config/routes.rb
        Views:      plugins/things/app/views/things/index.html.slim [...]
        Helper:     plugins/things/app/helpers/application_helper.rb

